# One DeepSeek API key per line, no quotes.
# 10 keys are recommended (one per worker thread); fewer is OK but you'll
# need to lower `concurrency.workers` in configs/online.yaml accordingly.
#
# Lines starting with '#' are comments and are skipped.
#
# To use this template:
#   1. Copy:  cp configs/deepseek_api-key.txt.example configs/deepseek_api-key.txt
#   2. Replace the placeholders below with your real keys.
#   3. The framework loads it automatically.
#
# Get keys at: https://platform.deepseek.com/api_keys

sk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
sk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
sk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
